This paper is primarily focused on increasing trust in AI services through the use of FactSheets, which contain information related to the purpose, performance, safety, security, and provenance of the AI service. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI. Additionally, the paper discusses the importance of safety and security, which could place it in the cs.CY and cs.CR categories, respectively. The paper also suggests a comprehensive set of declaration items, which could fall under the cs.SE category. Finally, the paper discusses the potential impact on consumers, which could place it in the cs.HC category.
